\c 75 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 75\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Abbaa Firdii Qajeelaa Ta'uu Isaatiif Waaqayyoon Galateeffachuu(Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kun akka qooqa faarfannaa isa "Hin balleessin" jedhamuutti faarfatame; faarfannaa Asaaf; weedduu)
\m \bd 1\bd* Nuyi si galateeffanna, yaa Waaqayyo, nuyi si galateeffanna! Ati maqaa kee isa beekamaadhaan warra gocha kee isa dinqisiisaa himanitti dhi'oo dha.
\m \bd 2\bd* Waaqayyo, "Yeroon murtoo godhee dhaabe sanatti, firdii qajeelaa nan kenna.
\m \bd 3\bd* lafti, warri lafa irra jiraatan hundinuus iddoo isaanii yommuu gad dhiisan, utuboota lafichaa jabeessee kan eegu ana" in jedha.
\m \bd 4\bd* Warra of jajaniin, "Of hin jajinaa!" Warra jal'ootaanis, "Gaanfa mataa keessanii irra-keessa hin qabatinaa.
\m \bd 5\bd* Gaanfa mataa keessanii ol hin qabatinaa! Morma yaafachuudhaanis hin dubbatinaa!" nan jedha.
\m \bd 6\bd* Nama ol qabuun ba'a-biiftuutii, lixa-biiftuutii, lafa duwwaatiis hin dhufu.
\m \bd 7\bd* firdii kan kennu immoo Waaqayyoo dha, isa tokko gad in deebisa, isa kaanis ol in qaba.
\m \bd 8\bd* Waaqayyo xoofoo daadhii waynii makaa qabu isa hoomachaa'u of harkaa qaba; inni daadhii waynichaa isa firdiif kennamu irraa in buusa, jal'oonni lafa irra jiran hundinuu isa in dhugu, siicoo isaa wajjinis isa in xururfatu.
\m \bd 9\bd* Ani garuu bara baraan kana nan labsa, Waaqayyoon isa kan Yaaqoob faarfannaadhaan nan jajadha;
\m \bd 10\bd* inni mataa jal'ootaa hundumaa irraa gaanfa in cira, gaanfi mataa warra qajeelotaa garuu ol in qabama.
\b 
